{
  "texts": [
    "[29] explained their industrial experiences, justifying the migration from a centralized data warehouse to a decentralized data mesh architecture.",
    "In their case, data were primarily used within domains.",
    "Inter-domain requests are served by a central metadata catalog, but datasharing mechanisms were not provided.",
    "More recently, [30] conducted a gray literature survey of 114 industry articles to provide a comprehensive review of data mesh.",
    "Moreover, they compared the service-oriented architecture to the data mesh due to their similarities."
  ]
}